sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant View as RequestDevicePage
    participant Dialog as BorrowDialog
    participant VM as ViewModel
    participant UC as BorrowDeviceUseCase
    participant DB as SQLite

    User->>View: Click Borrow trên dòng model
    View->>Dialog: Hiển thị ContentDialog
    Note over Dialog: Model, Manufacturer, Category<br/>Available: 5<br/>Quantity: NumberBox 1-5
    User->>Dialog: Chọn quantity = 3, click Confirm
    Dialog->>VM: BorrowCommand(modelId, quantity)
    VM->>UC: ExecuteAsync(modelId, quantity, instanceId)
    UC->>DB: BEGIN IMMEDIATE transaction
    Note over DB: Check Available >= 3<br/>UPDATE Available, Reserved<br/>INSERT 3 BorrowedDevice
    DB-->>UC: Success
    UC-->>VM: Result
    VM->>VM: SyncService.Broadcast
    VM->>VM: Reload trang hiện tại
